reviewText: Love the movie, only wish it were also available with English subtitles.

This movie is a good film. The version with English subtitles is rated PG-13, but for some reason this one is rated G. It really should be PG-13. I will be showing this movie to my Spanish IV class, but I will skip over a few of the PG-13 parts at the beginning.
Esta excelente la pelicula, bien hecha, excelente guion,fluida e increiblemente natural
Purchased as a gift.  I watched the American theatre version.  Thought it was a good story and comical.  Going to need tissues.
Es una hermosa pelicula. Muy pocas me han hecho llorar pero de alegria y de tristeza. Si que valio la pena comprarla =)
The best movie !!!! I recomend to see to everybody, its a family movie, and the actors are very wonderful!!!
Another fantastically funny movie with Eugenio Derbez!
GREAT movie. Have watched it at least a dozen times and enjoy it every time. It seems predictable, but is anything but.

Out of all the movies I showed to my Spanish classes this is their FAVORITE.  I have seen it numerous times and I will watch it many more times.  It is just that good!!!! Awesome movie!! Highly recommended!!!
Fast shipping. Good movie at a good price.
Great movie, you will enjoy it!
